window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Kristjan was visiting with nobles and royalty at an undisclosed location when his meeting was interrupted by an assassination attempt on the royals. </b></p> <p>Fortunately, the attempt was thwarted, but Kristjan was severely injured in the process. He surrounded himself within a barrier to try and heal himself, but no one knows where he is or if he lives. </p> <p>Will Kristjan succumb to his injuries, or will his bonded step in and help?</p> <p><i>This book is intended for mature audiences due to cursing, unconventional relationships, and violence within.</i></p>"; 
